        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "他們說“求你為我們立一個王治理我們”這件事，使撒母耳很不高興，他就禱告耶和華。"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "撒母耳不喜悅他們說「立一個王治理我們」，他就禱告耶和華。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "But the thing was displeasing in the sight of Samuel when they said, “Give us a king to judge us.” And Samuel prayed to the Lord."
